#  Node.js Payment Processing System with RabbitMQ

This is a beginner-friendly project that demonstrates how to build a simple payment processing system using **Node.js**, **Express**, and **RabbitMQ** with **retry logic**. The system simulates asynchronous background payment handling and supports retrying failed jobs.

---

##  Features

-  Asynchronous payment queue with RabbitMQ
-  Fast API response (no blocking)
-  Auto-retry failed payment tasks (up to 3 times)
-  Modular structure (Producer & Consumer)
-  Testable using Postman

---

## Tech Stack

- [Node.js](https://nodejs.org)
- [Express](https://expressjs.com)
- [RabbitMQ](https://www.rabbitmq.com/)
- [amqplib](https://www.npmjs.com/package/amqplib)

---

